./sdp/prd-snapshot.md:76:- **New** `my-claw/tests/test_sampler_integration.py` — end-to-end composer → selector → OSC dispatch
./sdp/prd-snapshot.md:77:- **Extended** `my-claw/tools/senseweave/artist_identity.py` — `SIGNATURE_VOICES = (..., "sw_sampler")`; per-mode `sampler_density` field
