n hardening item.\\\\n+4. **Pre-existing (out of scope)**: Critique/revision integration test still outstanding from prior hardening checklist.\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/logs/self-repair.log b/sdp/logs/self-repair.log\\\\nindex 591bd15..db9b41b 100644\\\\n--- a/sdp/logs/self-repair.log\\\\n+++ b/sdp/logs/self-repair.log\\\\n@@ -61,3 +61,17 @@\\\\n 2026-04-16T05:43:57.478013+00:00 | orphan_process_cleanup | ok | killed 0 process(es)\\\\n 2026-04-16T05:43:57.478038+00:00 | migrations | ok | schema verified\\\\n 2026-04-16T05:43:57.478063+00:00 | task_disappearance_restore | ok | 65 task(s) present\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.042312+00:00 | integrity_check | ok | ok\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.043092+00:00 | wal_mode | ok | wal -> wal\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.043126+00:00 | running_tasks_reset | ok | reset 0 task(s)\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.043151+00:00 | open_task_run_cleanup | ok | closed 0 open task run(s)\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.043176+00:00 | orphan_process_cleanup | ok | killed 0 process(es)\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.043200+00:00 | migrations | ok | schema verified\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:20:55.043222+00:00 | task_disappearance_restore | ok | 105 task(s) present\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.527742+00:00 | integrity_check | ok | ok\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.528095+00:00 | wal_mode | ok | wal -> wal\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.528127+00:00 | running_tasks_reset | ok | reset 0 task(s)\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.528156+00:00 | open_task_run_cleanup | ok | closed 0 open task run(s)\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.528183+00:00 | orphan_process_cleanup | ok | killed 0 process(es)\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.528209+00:00 | migrations | ok | schema verified\\\\n+2026-04-16T18:21:42.528234+00:00 | task_disappearance_restore | ok | 105 task(s) present\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/notifications.log b/sdp/notifications.log\\\\nindex eaf25ab..d2c729f 100644\\\\n--- a/sdp/notifications.log\\\\n+++ b/sdp/notifications.log\\\\n@@ -215,3 +215,17 @@\\\\n {\\\\\\\"agent\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"codex\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"duration\\\\\\\"